Given  User creates POST Request for the Dietician  API endpoint with "patient" and "Post_Patient_Valid"
When  User sends HTTPS Request and  request Body with mandatory fields and morbidity files from "patient" with "Post_Patient_Valid"
Then  User receives response for POST "patient" with "Post_Patient_Valid"
